-- Stefanel Sets Final Terms on Rights Offering Guaranteed by UniCredit, IMI
-- Jerrold Colten
-- 2010-07-01T06:55:29Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-01/stefanel-sets-final-terms-on-rights-offering-guaranteed-by-unicredit-imi.html

          
          
             Stefanel SpA, an Italian maker and
retailer of of leisure clothing, said in a statement that it
will sell up to 81 million new shares at 61.5 euro cents each,
34 percent below the theoretical ex-rights price.  
 The share sale will run from July 5 to July 23, the company
said. Investors will receive rights to 25 new shares for each
share owned, according to the statement.  
          
          


  


        